#Text=Andy Martin : I did indeed found the “ Birther ” movement questioning Barack
#Text=Obama ’s origins in Hawai’i but because of the need to run a national campaign for president I have not been active in examining Obama ’s latest birth certificate .
#Text=I think it was/is enough that I started the movement that ultimately forced Obama to release a document .
#Text=I know there has been controversy about the new document but I am not involved in that controversy .
#Text=It is for others to study and comment on the latest certificate ; I am a full-time presidential candidate for the foreseeable future .
#Text=( (
#Text=WSS
#Text=) )
#Text=: You have stated that it is your personal opinion that Frank Marshall Davis is the father of Barack Obama . What specifically led to this opinion ?
#Text=Martin : My personal opinion that Frank Marshall Davis is Barack Obama ’s biological father is based on my extensive research in Hawai’i .
#Text=( (
#Text=WSS
#Text=) )
#Text=: Where specifically did you obtain the material for your research and what did it entail ?
#Text=Martin :
#Text=Because my Obama research in Hawai’i is ongoing and will be continuing in a research trip later this year I do not discuss my sources or methods of investigation .
#Text=My writing speaks for itself .
#Text=( (
#Text=WSS
#Text=) )
#Text=:
#Text=Since announcing he would not seek the Republican nomination , Donald Trump seems to have toned down his statements on the birth certificate issue .
#Text=What are your current views on Donald Trump ?
#Text=Martin : I did not pay a lot of attention to Donald Trump ’s “ campaign ” for president because his behavior seemed to suggest it was a charade .
#Text=Mr. Trump has destroyed his political viability by saying initially he would only run as a Republican and then repudiating himself and suggesting he might run as an independent .
#Text=Public leadership is serious business ; Mr. Trump has shown he is not serious .
#Text=( (
#Text=WSS
#Text=) )
#Text=How would [ you ] assess the Obama presidency ?
#Text=Martin :
#Text=The Obama presidency is an abject failure .
#Text=I predicted Mr. Obama would fail in a Psychological Profile which was the first chapter of my book Obama : The Man Behind The Mask .
#Text=Obama ’s failure is no surprise to me .
#Text=( (
#Text=WSS
#Text=) )
#Text=Do you believe Obama has done any good things as president ?
#Text=Martin : I ca n’t think of any off the top
#Text=( (
#Text=WSS
#Text=) )
#Text=You ask Barack Obama to resign and want Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid to take over .
#Text=What legal precedent forms the basis of this ?
#Text=And assuming Vice President Biden resigns as well , why should Speaker John Boehner not take over as president ?
#Text=Martin : The president of the Senate is third , not the speaker , so Reid is a practical choice . [ Editor 's note 1 ]
#Text=Boehner is fourth . [ Editor 's note 2 ]
#Text=Personal past
#Text=Martin was asked several questions about his personal past , which he declined to answer .
#Text=He refused to discuss his two previous presidential campaigns , his past affiliation with the Democratic Party and would not say which candidates he supported in previous elections .
#Text=When pressed , Martin stated that the questions were irrelevant .
